    "en": {
      "title": "There will be a three-hour power cut tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has approved the Ceylon Electricity Board to carry out a 3-hour power cut tomorrow (22). This three-hour power cut comes into effect after the failure of the first generators at the Norochchola power plant. A power cut of 1 hour and 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour and 20 minutes during the night is scheduled."
      ],
